__data__.text: Resembling the familiar goblins but with pig-like heads, they are affectionately referred to as Bokoblins. They are categorized into several types: Stalk Bokoblin, Bokoblin, Blue Bokoblin, Black Bokoblin, Silver Bokoblin, and Gold Bokoblin. The first two types only drop their horns and teeth. Blue and Black Bokoblins drop an extra liver. Silver and Gold Bokoblins are relatively rare in the game, dropping various parts as well as precious items like Amber, Sapphire, Ruby, and Diamond.
